; Lazyload Smoke Test
; Purpose: verify CALLSTR can trigger on-demand loading of a delayed function.
; Setup: place this file in erb/00_TITLE.ERB, and 99_DELAYED.ERB in erb/LAZY/.
; lazyloading.cfg must list "LAZY" as a lazy-load subdirectory.
; Expected output (first screen):
;   === LAZYLOAD SMOKE ===
;   PASS: title file loaded
;   PASS: lazy target loaded
;   PASS: lazyload smoke finished
;   [WAIT prompt]

@EVENTFIRST
PRINTL === LAZYLOAD SMOKE ===
PRINTL PASS: title file loaded
CALLSTR "LAZY_TARGET"
PRINTL PASS: lazyload smoke finished
WAIT
RETURN 0
